code: import axios from'./axiosConfig';export const getAlerts=async()=>{return await axios.get('/alerts');};export const getAlertById=async id=>{return await axios.get("/alerts/".concat(id));};export const createAlert=async alertData=>{return await axios.post('/alerts',alertData);};export const updateAlert=async(id,alertData)=>{return await axios.put("/alerts/".concat(id),alertData);};export const deleteAlert=async id=>{return await axios.delete("/alerts/".concat(id));};
